  "prompt": "Have my wounds gone infected?",
  "response": "I'm not a doctor, but there are some signs you can look for to determine if a wound might be infected. Common symptoms of infection include:\n\n- Increased redness around the wound\n- Swelling and warmth at the site\n- Pus or drainage\n- Increased pain or tenderness\n- Fever or chills\n\nIf you notice any of these symptoms, it\u2019s important to consult a healthcare professional for an accurate diagnosis and appropriate treatment.",
